            "Ask one normal-sounding question.",
            "Let small confusion show through."
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "overconfident",
          "context": "You think you understand this era better than you do. Your confidence makes your mistakes more obvious.",
          "base_directives": [
            "Use one wrong assumption about everyday life.",
            "Act like the mistake was intentional.",
            "Keep moving instead of explaining too much."
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "homesick",
          "context": "You miss your own time and are starting to feel lonely. You still try to be pleasant.",
          "base_directives": [
            "Let one detail from your time slip out.",
            "Do not monologue about the future.",
            "Respond to the other person's emotion first."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "sentiment": {
      "required": true,
      "template_vars": [],
